Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.61,0:00:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以无法回应你的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧 然后 不要再出现在我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:44.98,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}Love, I've got to feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:48.22,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}If you put your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:51.63,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}I know what my life would be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:56.84,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}Oh, you are all I ever need
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.54,0:01:02.51,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}I try to hear what you say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.21,0:01:04.67,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}So I pray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:08.26,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}But you're fading away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:15.43,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}Don't go and break my fragile heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:18.96,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}We won't fall apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:27.03,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}'Cause you're my only star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:32.84,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}I wonder why my tears come at night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:36.28,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}Calling you, so like a little child
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:39.55,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}All the things you have in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:42.96,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}I wish I could say your insides
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:45.97,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}My love, you've got to feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:49.50,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}And if we put our trust in you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:53.08,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}You know what our lives would be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:02:00.39,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}Oh, you are the one I believe
