Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同班同学翻了我的包
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包？
